Interface ReactiveUniqueEntityLoader

    public interface ReactiveUniqueEntityLoader
extends org.hibernate.loader.entity.UniqueEntityLoader
    A reactific UniqueEntityLoader, the contract implemented by all reactive entity loaders, including batch loaders.
